@startuml 05-merchant-payment
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Thanh toán Merchant (có phí nền tảng 10%)

show footbox

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC
skinparam noteBorderColor #C0A030

actor "Người dùng" as User
participant "Front-end" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Transaction\nService" as TS
participant "User Service" as US
participant "Wallet Service" as WS
database "transaction_db" as TDB
database "user_db" as UDB
database "wallet_db" as WDB
queue "ActiveMQ\n(transaction-notification)" as MQ
participant "Notification\nService" as NS

== 1. Mở trang Payment - tải danh sách dịch vụ ==
User -> FE : Vào trang "Thanh toán dịch vụ"

FE -> GW : GET /api/v1/merchants/types
GW -> US : GET /api/merchants/types
US --> FE : List<{ code, description }>

FE -> GW : GET /api/v1/merchants/list
GW -> US : GET /api/merchants/list
US -> UDB : SELECT merchants WHERE active = true
UDB --> US : merchant list
US --> FE : List<MerchantListResponse>

FE -> GW : GET /api/v1/wallets/my-balance\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>

note right of GW #E3F2FD
  /merchants/types & /list: whitelist (không JWT).
  /wallets/my-balance: AuthGlobalFilter decode JWT,
  validate jti, inject X-User-Id/Role/Phone.
end note

GW -> WS : GET /api/wallets/my-balance + header nội bộ
WS -> WDB : SELECT wallet WHERE user_id = ?
WDB --> WS : wallet
WS --> FE : { balance, walletId }

FE --> User : Hiển thị grid merchant + balance

== 2. Người dùng chọn merchant & nhập số tiền ==
User -> FE : Click merchant → mở modal thanh toán

note right of FE #FFF3E0
  **FE tính phí theo loại merchant:**
  PARKING tự động theo giờ (3k/5k/10k);
  loại khác user tự nhập amount.
end note

User -> FE : Nhập số tiền + ghi chú → "Tiếp tục"

note right of FE #E8F5E9
  **FE validate:** amount ≥ 1.000đ và ≤ balance (cached).
end note

User -> FE : Nhập mã PIN 6 số → "Xác nhận"

note right of FE #E8F5E9
  **FE chuẩn bị payload:** requestId = UUID v4
  (chống double-submit), kèm merchantId/Name/Phone.
end note

== 3. Gateway xác thực JWT ==
FE -> GW : POST /api/v1/transactions/merchant/payment\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>\n{ requestId, merchantId, merchantName,\n  merchantPhone, amount, description, pin }

note right of GW #E3F2FD
  **AuthGlobalFilter:** decode JWT → check blacklist jti
  → inject X-User-Id/Role/Phone + X-Internal-Secret.
end note

GW -> US : GET /internal/users/validate?jti=...
US -> UDB : SELECT invalidated_tokens WHERE jti = ?
UDB --> US : (rỗng → token còn hiệu lực)
US --> GW : 200 OK

== 4. Transaction Service xử lý ==
GW -> TS : POST /api/transactions/merchant/payment\nX-User-Phone: ***

alt fromPhone == merchantPhone (tự thanh toán)
    TS --> FE : 400 SELF_TRANSFER
end

== 4.1 Idempotency check ==
TS -> TDB : SELECT transactions WHERE request_id = ?

note right of TS #FFEBEE
  **Chống double-submit:** SUCCESS/FAILED → trả kết quả cũ;
  PENDING → 400 DUPLICATE_TRANSACTION.
end note

== 4.2 Xác thực PIN ==
TS -> US : POST /internal/users/verify-pin\nX-Internal-Secret: ***\n{ phone, pin }

note right of US #FFEBEE
  **PIN check + chống brute-force:** BCrypt match,
  sai 5 lần → khoá PIN 15 phút; đúng → reset attempts.
end note

US -> UDB : check + update pin_failed_attempts
UDB --> US : ok
alt PIN sai hoặc bị khoá
    US --> TS : 400 INVALID_PIN / PIN_LOCKED
    TS --> FE : 400 PIN_VERIFICATION_FAILED
    FE --> User : Hiển thị lỗi PIN
end
US --> TS : 200 OK

== 4.3 Lấy thông tin sender + merchant ==
TS -> US : POST /internal/users/batch\n{ phones: [fromPhone, merchantPhone] }
US -> UDB : SELECT users WHERE phone IN (...)
UDB --> US : 2 users
US --> TS : [fromUser, toUser]

note right of TS #FFF3E0
  **Kiểm tra:** sender/recipient không LOCKED,
  sender.kycStatus == VERIFIED.
end note

alt Sender/Recipient khoá hoặc chưa KYC
    TS --> FE : 400 KYC_NOT_VERIFIED / SENDER_LOCKED / RECIPIENT_LOCKED
end

== 4.4 Tính phí nền tảng ==
TS -> US : GET /internal/users/first-admin
US -> UDB : SELECT user WHERE role = ADMIN LIMIT 1
UDB --> US : admin user
US --> TS : adminUser

note right of TS #FFF3E0
  **Tính phí (feeRate = 10%):**
  Case A (admin ≠ customer): fee = amount × 0.10,
    txAmount = amount → /transfer-with-fee (3-party).
  Case B (admin tự pay): fee = 0,
    txAmount = amount × 0.9 → /transfer (2-party).
end note

== 4.5 Tạo transaction PENDING ==
note right of TS #FFEBEE
  saveAndFlush để bắt race condition khi 2 request
  cùng requestId song song (UNIQUE constraint).
end note

alt INSERT thành công
    TS -> TDB : INSERT transactions\n(status = PENDING, type = PAYMENT,\n merchantId, amount = txAmount, fee)
    TDB --> TS : transactionId
else DataIntegrityViolation (race condition)
    TS -> TDB : SELECT tx WHERE request_id = ?
    TDB --> TS : tx (đã thắng race)
    TS --> FE : Trả kết quả cũ (nếu đã final)\nhoặc 400 DUPLICATE_TRANSACTION
end

== 4.6 Gọi wallet-service trừ/cộng tiền ==

alt Case A: admin ≠ customer → 3-party
    TS -> WS : POST /internal/wallets/transfer-with-fee\n{ fromUserId, toUserId (merchant),\n  platformUserId (admin), amount, fee,\n  transactionId, note }

    note right of WS #FFEBEE
      **transferWithFee:** idempotency by transactionId;
      lock 3 ví theo UUID order ascending (tránh deadlock);
      edge case fee=0 hoặc platform trùng → fallback /transfer.
    end note

    WS -> WDB : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE 3 wallets
    WDB --> WS : 3 wallets

    note right of WS #FFF3E0
      **Kiểm tra:** 3 ví không LOCKED; reset daily/monthly
      limit nếu sang kỳ mới; balance + limit ≥ amount (full).
    end note

    alt Wallet thành công
        note right of WS #E8F5E9
          **Split:** customer −= amount; merchant += amount − fee;
          admin += fee. (3 ledger entries cùng transactionId.)
        end note
        WS -> WDB : UPDATE 3 wallets + INSERT 3 ledger\n  DEBIT customer (PAYMENT),\n  CREDIT merchant (PAYMENT),\n  CREDIT admin (PLATFORM_FEE)
        WDB --> WS : ok
        WS --> TS : 200 "Thanh toán thành công"
    else Wallet fail (số dư/hạn mức/ví khoá)
        WS --> TS : 400 INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE / LIMIT_EXCEEDED / WALLET_LOCKED
    end
else Case B: admin == customer → 2-party
    TS -> WS : POST /internal/wallets/transfer\n{ fromUserId, toUserId, amount = txAmount,\n  transactionId, reason = "PAYMENT" }

    note right of WS #FFF3E0
      **transfer 2-party:** idempotency, lock 2 ví theo UUID,
      check balance/limit, UPDATE + ghi 2 ledger (DEBIT/CREDIT).
    end note

    alt Wallet thành công
        WS -> WDB : Lock 2 ví, UPDATE + 2 ledger entries
        WDB --> WS : ok
        WS --> TS : 200 OK
    else Wallet fail
        WS --> TS : 400 INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE / LIMIT_EXCEEDED / WALLET_LOCKED
    end
end

== 4.7 Finalize transaction ==
alt Wallet trả về SUCCESS
    TS -> TDB : UPDATE status = SUCCESS + status_history
    note right of TS #E8F5E9
      **Đảm bảo nhất quán:** publish JMS **sau khi**
      DB commit (afterCommit) — tránh notification "ma".
    end note
    TS -> MQ : convertAndSend("transaction-notification",\nTransactionNotificationEvent)
    TS --> FE : 200 { transactionId, status, amount, fee, ... }
    FE --> User : "Thanh toán thành công" + refresh balance
else Wallet trả về error
    TS -> TDB : UPDATE status = FAILED + status_history (lý do)
    TS --> FE : 400 TRANSFER_FAILED + message
    FE --> User : Hiển thị lỗi
end

== 5. Thông báo bất đồng bộ ==
MQ -> NS : @JmsListener nhận event

note right of NS #FFF3E0
  Lưu 2 notification (sender DEBIT + merchant CREDIT),
  push WebSocket, gửi SMS (SpeedSMS) + Email (SendGrid).
end note

NS -> NS : Xử lý event

@enduml
